      "cookedHtml": "<p>Make can not only integrate tools like <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> and Salesforce, but can also act as the logic layer between the two allowing dozens of workflows to be created.</p>\n<p>Automating Processes Like:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/bulb.png?v=12\" title=\":bulb:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":bulb:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Inventory and Order Management<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/bulb.png?v=12\" title=\":bulb:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":bulb:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Customer Support and Ticketing<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/bulb.png?v=12\" title=\":bulb:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":bulb:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Analytics and Reporting<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/bulb.png?v=12\" title=\":bulb:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":bulb:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Marketing Campaigns and Lead Nurturing<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/bulb.png?v=12\" title=\":bulb:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":bulb:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Sales Quote and Proposal Generation<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/bulb.png?v=12\" title=\":bulb:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":bulb:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Assigning Leads and Sales Pipeline Management</p>\n<p>Continue to work smarter <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/clinking_glasses.png?v=12\" title=\":clinking_glasses:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":clinking_glasses:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><a class=\"hashtag-cooked\" href=\"/tag/make\"><span class=\"hashtag-icon-placeholder\"></span><span>make</span></a> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#Automation</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#Salesforce</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#Monday</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#WorkflowAutomation</span></p>"
